movies.title: Chappaquiddick
movies.plot: Ted Kennedy's life and political career become derailed in the aftermath of a fatal car accident in 1969 that claims the life of a young campaign strategist, Mary Jo Kopechne.

events.title: Ted Kennedy crashes his car, killing his passenger Mary Jo Kopechne
after crashing his car, Ted Kennedy flees the scene

movies.title: The Miracle Season
movies.plot: After the tragic death of star volleyball player Caroline "Line" Found, a team of dispirited high school girls must band together under the guidance of their tough-love coach in hopes of winning the state championship!
